V 2.x
-----
- UTF-8 encoding in DN where needed.
- Describe SSL-setup in server.
- Make to work with JDK 1.3, problems with importing certificate chains in jks
using keytool, as well as JDK 1.4 stuff.
- More automated testing, Junit as well as web-stuff.
- Make a database model similar to architecture model.
- Make public web more user friendly.
- Add a 'Service Locator' to concentrate code for lookups?
- Use a 'Value List Handler' for listing of all certificates, clrs and users?
- Better architecture for JSPs (MVC - ModelViewController?).
- Continue improving exceptions and error handling.
- Strategy for handling certificate issuance if notAfter is beyond CAs notAfter.
- Create Windows logon certificates, i.e. add "Extended Key Usage",
http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb;EN-US;q281245
- Implement SCEP, http://openscep.othello.ch/
- Test LDAP with mod_authz_ldap in apache
- Import utility to get users from external datasources.
- Virtual CAs multiple CAs within one deployment
- XML/Soap stuff.
- Multiple CDPs, comma separated strings should give several CDPs. 
- Better command line tools for batch stuff.

Future
------
- Issue smartcards
- Implement XKMS specifications
- Add support for deeper hierarchies than 2 levels of CAs (today only root and
CA).
- Run on other appservers, ie Websphere etc.
- Add smart card support (PKCS15) in CA for protection of private key.
- Make CA/RA for off-line authorization of requests for high security
environments.
- RA with self registration for end-entities, RA approves registration.
- OCSP
